Michael Leavitt (R), 42%
Merrill Cook (I), 34%
Stewart Hanson (D), 23%


1996 Race for Governor

Michael Leavitt (R) (inc.), 75%
Jim Bradley (D), 23%


2000 Race for Governor

Michael Leavitt (R) (inc.), 56%
Bill Orton (D), 42%



