2006 D.C. Circuit U.S. Court of Appeals Case Law




Arrington, Derreck v. USA, et al



Date:  December 29, 2006
Docket Number:  
						05-5263
								
									


Derrek E. Arrington, Appellant v. United States of America, et al., Appellees



Date:  December 29, 2006
Citation: 
473 F.3d 329




Lakhdar Boumediene, Detainee, Camp Delta, et al., Appellants v. George W. Bush, President of the United States, et al., Appellees.khaled A.f. al Odah, Next Friend of Fawzi Khalid Abdullah Fahad al Odah et al., Appellants v. United States of America, et al., Appellees



Date:  December 29, 2006
Citation: 
476 F.3d 934




Lakhdar Boumediene, Detainee, Camp Delta, et al., Appellants v. George W. Bush, President of the United States, et al., Appellees.khaled A.f. al Odah, Next Friend of Fawzi Khalid Abdullah Fahad al Odah et al., Appellants v. United States of America, et al., Appellees



Date:  December 29, 2006
Citation: 
476 F.3d 934




S Coast Air Qlty v. EPA



Date:  December 22, 2006
Docket Number:  
						04-1200
								
									


Williston Basin v. FERC



Date:  December 22, 2006
Docket Number:  
						05-1209
								
									


USA v. Gewin, Barry



Date:  December 22, 2006
Docket Number:  
						05-3086
								
									


Baker Hostetler v. COMM



Date:  December 22, 2006
