Room Accommodations
We are excited to return to the Grand America Hotel, a landmark in Salt Lake City, for our general sessions. Leavitt Partners has a negotiated discount rate at the Grand America Hotel for our event.  To book a room at the Grand America, please click the link below or call group reservations at 800-437-5288.
Our pre-conference meetings will be held at the Marriott City Center in Salt Lake City. The Marriott City Center is a 15-minute walk to the Grand America hotel. Due to limited availability at the Grand America on Wednesday July 15, 2015 we have negotiated a discount rate at the Marriott City Center for guests coming in early for the Pre-Conference. To book a room at the Marriott City Center, please click the link below or call group reservations (800) 228-9290 and mention Leavitt Partners
